<span style="font-size: large;"><b>*** WORLD CENTRAL KITCHEN ----- FOOD IS A UNIVERSAL HUMAN RIGHT</b></span>

<a href="https://wck.org/">https://wck.org/</a>

This is self explanatory…… GET A MEAL - “Our team is working alongside local associations and community leaders to facilitate safe and efficient food distribution. As our kitchen capacity grows, we remain steadfast in our commitment to serve the people”

“Relief Team is in Southern California to support first responders and families impacted by wildfires in the Los Angeles area. Our teams have mobilized across the region to provide immediate relief in the form of sandwiches and water as we identify all areas of need. Several WCK Chef Corps members are on standby, ready to provide comforting meals. “

<a href="https://wck.org/news/first-alert-ca-fires-jan25">https://wck.org/news/first-alert-ca-fires-jan25</a>

